query:
SELECT 
  serviceType,
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN rateUsdCents IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_price,
  SUM(CASE WHEN rateUsdCents IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_price
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 12
GROUP BY serviceType
